def count_character_in_final_string(s: str, k: int, n: int, c: str) -> int:
    len_s = len(s)
    full_reps = n / len_s
    partial_len = n % len_s
    count_in_full_rep = s.count(c)
    count_in_partial_rep = s[:partial_len].count(c)
    total_count = count_in_full_rep * full_reps + count_in_partial_rep
    return total_count
